    "Many Fig. 4 Strategies for biomaterial integration and life cycle considerations in the low-carbon buildings.",
    "This figure shows the multifaceted strategies essential for transitioning to a low-carbon building milieu through biomaterial usage.",
    "It underscores the importance of strategies being deeply embedded in life cycle considerations and systematic thinking from an owner's perspective.",
    "The emphasis is the necessity for both financial and legislative stimuli to extend the lifespan of structures, thereby fostering the adoption of biomaterials in low-carbon renovations and refurbishments.",
    "The diagram also stresses the need for all stakeholders in the building materials sector to fully comprehend the environmental impact of their material choices across the building's life cycle."
